          <li><a href="https://github.com/Deroy2112/proxmox-lxc-templates/releases" target="_blank">All Releases</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/Deroy2112/proxmox-lxc-templates/tree/main/templates" target="_blank">Source Code</a></li>
